    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/20700f430d9ff3236ca9d23b39923391.avif?t=1760692872\" width=1560 height=195 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;Treat or Trick⭐&gt; </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>万圣漫游乐队</strong>》是一款以万圣节为主题的<strong>剧情向节奏动作冒险游戏</strong>。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;见习死神的行进乐队组建记&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/bf2d9cb95673165e26bcd117636fe4f4.poster.avif?t=1760692872\" width=1054 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/bf2d9cb95673165e26bcd117636fe4f4.webm?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/bf2d9cb95673165e26bcd117636fe4f4.mp4?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见习死神<strong>廖悠</strong>为执行死神部的任务，被派往<strong>万圣奇境</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，面对堆积如山的文书工作，她感到厌倦，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是决定放下工作，追逐自己长久以来的梦想——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加万圣节游行，并组建属于自己的行进乐队「<strong>万圣漫游乐队</strong>」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;与故事同行的节奏游戏&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/9ede76df6946b410f2caa4c95d7204ac.poster.avif?t=1760692872\" width=1054 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/9ede76df6946b410f2caa4c95d7204ac.webm?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/9ede76df6946b410f2caa4c95d7204ac.mp4?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏分为<strong>剧集部分</strong>和<strong>冒险部分</strong>两种模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>剧集部分</strong>中，挑战融合动画与剧情的<strong>节奏游戏</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>冒险部分</strong>中，通过<strong>对话</strong>与<strong>探索</strong>推进故事，解锁全新的剧集。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;游行团的爆笑插曲&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/478b81d15281f93fa8e55a87cfaeef31.poster.avif?t=1760692872\" width=1054 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/478b81d15281f93fa8e55a87cfaeef31.webm?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/478b81d15281f93fa8e55a87cfaeef31.mp4?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>圆形轨道</strong>上出现的<strong>左右音符</strong>，请根据音乐节奏准确输入！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用简单的<strong>双键操作</strong>，每侧各有3个按键，只需按下其中一个即可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伴随输入反应的动画，欣赏角色们丰富多彩的<strong>剧集</strong>故事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;锵——！&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/3e289f85ed51a13ebdff76111589b22d.poster.avif?t=1760692872\" width=1054 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/3e289f85ed51a13ebdff76111589b22d.webm?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/3e289f85ed51a13ebdff76111589b22d.mp4?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当故事进入高潮时，会突然触发<strong>锵——！</strong>特别事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在此阶段，需要使用左右所有按键进行<strong>6键操作</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发挥你的反应力与专注力，克服每个章节中不同的<strong>锵事件</strong>挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&lt;聊一聊吧&gt;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/be18a7d026e801d53721a9c5c1a1b47e.poster.avif?t=1760692872\" width=1054 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/be18a7d026e801d53721a9c5c1a1b47e.webm?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127030/extras/be18a7d026e801d53721a9c5c1a1b47e.mp4?t=1760692872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>冒险部分</strong>中，通过<strong>对话</strong>与<strong>探索</strong>展开剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与性格鲜明的<strong>万圣节伙伴们</strong>相遇，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一同见证廖悠组建「<strong>万圣漫游乐队</strong>」的故事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
